{"tid":2378133,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍提高英語水平　確保對敵時準確展示立場","createTime":"2021-01-24T08:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T09:11:33.000Z","uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"04d1eb4aac0706de2f4011ecf9eef8408186249c","tid":2378133,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T08:05:47.000Z","msg":"駐守南海的解放軍官兵近日加強演練和提高英語水平，確保在對敵喊話中能準確展示立場。<br />\n<br />\n在南海執行戰備巡航任務的「呼和浩特」艦演練遇到可疑船隻時女兵用英語警告驅離，官兵又進行分隊對抗演習，演練對敵軍用英語喊話。<br />\n<br />\n這些隸屬南部戰區海軍部隊的前線官兵，央視形容他們是處於南海維權和維護地區和平穩定的最前沿，圍繞戰場需要英語能力成為必備的技能。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，解放軍平日會利用訓練的時間制定學習計劃，提高英語能力，片段見到他們學的不少是勸降的說話，能打仗，打勝仗之外，學好英語更能做到「不戰而屈人之兵」。<br />\n<br />\n隨着解放軍近年在部分有主權爭議的地區加強巡航和演練，與外國軍機或軍艦相遇的情況亦更頻繁，有海軍航空兵機師表示不只飛行技術要純熟，英語亦要說得流利才能做好溝通，避免誤判。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=421457&amp;hot=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D421457%26hot%3D1&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=d0c06ab2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D421457%26hot%3D1&h=d43e3e85\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=421457&amp;hot=1</a>"},{"pid":"7743a3543e230c9218ca4aa55bb90241f73b21e5","tid":2378133,"uid":298523,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T08:06:59.000Z","msg":"I go to ship by bus."},{"pid":"b0c742f15ac6babe057c9bf82fe2964f229c6d08","tid":2378133,"uid":125357,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T08:07:21.000Z","msg":"sir!<br />\nThis way"},{"pid":"51b4e34a73d397aa0134276fa62c2e735229ecb0","tid":2378133,"uid":133183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T08:08:38.000Z","msg":"sup"},{"pid":"97ab939a67c3bfff95c2c6bbfe08e353f02e3543","tid":2378133,"uid":135114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T08:08:4